fullplot: Jill and Joy find money on the street and buy Mrs Rosebud's house. The house is custom-made for two little girls. Jill and Joy start to enjoy the summer of their lives and make the acquaintance of two wondrous neighbour ladies Tinglestein and Tanglestein.
